long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: FormGem is a browser extension designed to help users automatically solve quizzes within Google Forms. It analyzes the questions in the form, interacts with the page elements, and uses Google Generative AI to generate and display answers with confidence scores. The extension is specifically focused on automating quiz solving in Google Forms, providing users with immediate assistance in answering multiple-choice, single-choice, and text-based questions.
